headline: POTTERY BARN TEEN LAUNCHES COLLABORATION WITH THE WOMEN’S NATIONAL BASKETBALL ASSOCIATION
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, June 20, 2025--Pottery Barn Teen, portfolio brand of Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (NYSE: WSM), the world’s largest digital-first, design-led and sustainable home retailer, announced today an exclusive home furnishings collaboration with the Women’s National Basketball Association (WNBA), the premiere women’s basketball league in the United States.
